::Firearm::

Firearm looks at Battera, raising one hand to her chin, turning her head to 
look at him.

"Hey, I trust ya," he says, smiling, "Don't worry about Rex, though, he 
doesn't trust anyone. But I don't think he hates ya. He didn't let me kill 
you, after all."
